      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAJOR QUEEN (1) drew a squeeze box and was game in defeat when a close third, 1.75 lengths from the winner Linda Lou (17.80) at this track. Nicely placed to grab a well-deserved win. SUPER SYMON (6) turned in a solid run last start over 305m at this track finishing 4th and beaten only 5 lengths (18.16). Won at his only start from this box. Has ability and is one of the better chances. SPECKED (2) was an all the way winner two back but last start drifted back and wound up strongly to finish a 3.5 lengths third at Angle Park (19.89). The form from her last run stacks up well. Expecting another good run. CADILLAC MAGIC (8) saluted at big odds last time, cannot be ruled out.",
